<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The summary is used not only on the book, but on Tor Books&apos; page for it, the Amazon listing, and the Barnes &amp; Noble listing.<br/><br/>Since so many people have <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The summary is used not only on the book, but on Tor Books' page for it, the Amazon listing, and the Barnes &amp; Noble listing.<br /><br />Since so many people have reported this, I truncated the original summary and replaced it with a summary/review from Publishers Weekly, which is both more detailed and (I believe) does not include the big spoiler.<br /><br />Thoughts on this change welcome.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
